      <p><strong>6.2</strong> By continuing to use the Service after amendments have been made, or by using it for any purpose, including but not limited to uploading images or altering them, the User confirms their acceptance of all terms and conditions set forth in this Agreement.</p>
    </TimeLineElement>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <p>This Agreement is executed in English and constitutes an official document between the administration of the Service and the User.</p>
